{"tid":1536613,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"風向撚 送頭撚 小黎呢套啦6月講到依家","createTime":"2019-09-03T16:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:52:52.000Z","uid":143514,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"986689edf4a855267f0a8580639b5c6f608ec09b","tid":1536613,"uid":143514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:39:30.000Z","msg":"呢一招冇用架啦 中計撚都收皮啦 風向撚同送頭撚都可以準備收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解你地隻手拍極都唔響 因為唔係個個都好似你地咁係屋企睇個直播就斷定前線勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你只不過係睇番記者直播比你地睇既野 記者影得曬咩 記者知前線內部計劃咩？<br />\n<br />\n記者唔知 你更加唔知 同埋最後唔該講野客氣啲<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係你地都要入埋麻包袋"},{"pid":"93e342f553d2759c0219750288c329486c97d8c6","tid":1536613,"uid":143514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:39:47.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a9e2689367588a548eccfc0f3c0178bbc84058ac","tid":1536613,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link ta